===Theme song===
*"[[Irresistible (Jessica Simpson song)|Irresistible]]" by American singer [[Jessica Simpson]] was the official theme song for the tournament. Simpson performed the song during halftime of the final match between Colombia and Mexico. CONMEBOL chose the song to introduce the tournament to a younger audience.  The song was a hit single in South America at the time.
*"[[Bulería (David Bisbal song)|Bulería]] by Spanish Singer [[David Bisbal]] for [[Univision]] coverage for Copa América 2001

