{{Infobox darts player | image = | name = Antony Lopez | fullname = | nickname = Hot Fuzz | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1987|2|14}}<ref>https://www.mastercaller.com/players/antony-lopez</ref> | birth_place = [[Gibraltar]] | death_date = | death_place = | hometown = [[Gibraltar]] | homecountry = Gibraltar | since = | darts = | laterality = Right-handed | music = "[[Bad Boys (Inner Circle song)|Bad Boys]]" by [[Inner Circle (band)|Inner Circle]] | BDO = | PDC = 2014– | currentrank = | BDO World = | World Masters = Last 144: 2017 | World Darts Trophy = | Int. Darts League = | PDC World = | Matchplay = | Grand Prix = | UK Open = | Vegas = | European = | Premier League = | US Open = | tournament = | resultyears = }} '''Antony Lopez''' (born 14 February 1987) is a [[Gibraltar]]ian [[darts]] player who plays in [[Professional Darts Corporation]] events.
A policeman on [[Gibraltar]], he has qualified for the five most recent editions of the Gibraltar Darts Trophy, only winning one game, against another Gibraltarian in [[John Duo]].
