The '''Colombian Cycling Federation''' or '''FCC''' ({{Lang-es|Federación Colombiana de Ciclismo}}) is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Colombia]].

The FCC is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and [[Confederacion Panamericana de Ciclismo|COPACI]].

==External links==
* {{Official website|http://federacioncolombianadeciclismo.com}}

