'''Isidoro Beaton Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Belmopan]], [[Belize]].  It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of the Belizean football clubs [[Belmopan Blaze]] and [[Belmopan Bandits]]. The stadium is able to hold 2,500 people. It is also the most common used Belize National Football Team Home Venue.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/venues/belize/isidoro-beaton-stadium/v14266/|title=Isidoro Beaton Stadium|publisher=Uk.soccerway.com|accessdate=1 January 2015}}</ref>

