{{Infobox cricket ground | ground_name = Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club Ground | nickname = | country = England | image = | location = [[Kirby Muxloe]], [[Leicestershire]] | establishment = 1952 (first recorded match) | seating_capacity = | end1 = | end2 = | year1 = | club1 = | date = 23 August | year = 2010 | source = https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/577.html Ground profile }}
'''Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club Ground''' is a [[cricket]] ground in [[Kirby Muxloe]], [[Leicestershire]]. The first recorded match on the ground was in 1952, when the [[Leicestershire County Cricket Club|Leicestershire Second XI]] played the [[Nottinghamshire County Cricket Club|Nottinghamshire Second XI]].<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/577_misc.html Other matches played on Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club Ground]</ref> In addition, the ground has also held 2 [[Second XI Championship]] matches.<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/577_sec.html Second XI Championship Matches played on Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club Ground]</ref>
The ground held its first [[Women's One Day International cricket|Women's One Day International]] in the [[1973 Women's Cricket World Cup]] between [[International XI women's cricket team|International XI women]] and [[Jamaican women's cricket team|Jamaica women]]. The next held 2 Women's ODI's in the 1990 Women's European Championship when [[Denmark women's cricket team|Denmark women]] played [[Ireland women's cricket team|Ireland women]] and finally with [[England women's cricket team|England women]] playing Ireland women, in what is to date the final Women's ODI held at the ground.<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Grounds/11/577.html Women's One-Day International Matches played on Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club Ground]</ref>
In local domestic cricket, the ground is the home venue of [[Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club]].<ref>[http://www.team-m8.com/leicesterivanhoe/ Leicester Ivanhoe Cricket Club]{{dead link|date=December 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> who play in the [[Leicestershire Premier Cricket League]].
